ExamForge
ExamForge is an offline-first examination management system that enables teachers and administrators to manage question banks, generate examination papers, synchronize data across devices, and export professional PDF documents.
Technology Stack
Mobile
	•	React Native
	•	TypeScript
	•	SQLite
Backend
	•	ASP.NET Core
	•	Clean Architecture
	•	Entity Framework Core
	•	PostgreSQL
Document Generation
	•	QuestPDF
Core Features
	•	Offline-first mobile experience
	•	Local SQLite persistence
	•	Background synchronization
	•	Question bank management
	•	Subject management
	•	Exam paper generation
	•	PDF export
	•	Role-based authorization
	•	Conflict detection and resolution
